OL,3,CLuke Littler applies to trademark his
OL,4,Cface to combat AI fakes
OL,6,FLuke Littler has applied to trademark
OL,7,Fhis face in a bid to stop AI fakes.
OL,9,FThe teenage dart sensation made the
OL,10,Fapplication with the Intellectual
OL,11,FProperty Office to prevent fake
OL,12,Fproducts, powered by AI, using his
OL,13,Fpicture without permission and
OL,14,Fbreaking copyright laws.
OL,16,FThe 19-year-old, who has already
OL,17,Ftrademarked his "the Nuke" nickname in
OL,18,Fthe United States, appears on a wide
OL,19,Fvariety of branded products - from his
OL,20,Fown dart board to computer games and
OL,21,Fbags of nuts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
