OL,3,CLuke Littler applies to trademark his
OL,4,Cface to combat AI fakes
OL,6,FLittler, who has won back-to-back
OL,7,FWorld Championship titles, continues
OL,8,Fto rise as he won the night seven of
OL,9,Fthe Premier League in Dublin on 19
OL,10,FMarch.
OL,12,FHe admitted he is "still learning not
OL,13,Fto react to the fans" after silencing
OL,14,Fthe boos with an astonishing comeback
OL,15,Fin the final.
OL,26,@tD@SOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
