PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774033869
OL,3,CLuke Littler applies to trademark his
OL,4,Cface to combat AI fakes
OL,6,FWhile the biggest jeers of the night
OL,7,Fwere reserved for Northern Ireland's
OL,8,FJosh Rock, whose every throw was booed
OL,9,Fas his miserable Premier League form
OL,10,Fcontinued, Littler also drew the ire
OL,11,Fof the crowd.
OL,13,FBut Littler who hit out at hecklers
OL,14,Ffollowing a win over Rob Cross at the
OL,15,FPDC World Championship in December,
OL,16,Fhad the last laugh after coming from 5-
OL,17,F0 down in the final to beat Welshman
OL,18,FGerwyn Price 6-5.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
