OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774033869
OL,3,CLuke Littler applies to trademark his
OL,4,Cface to combat AI fakes
OL,6,FAfter avoiding a whitewash, Littler,
OL,7,Ffrom Warrington, celebrated
OL,8,Fsarcastically and then when trailing 5-
OL,9,F1 waved goodbye only for Price to miss
OL,10,Fthree match darts before the teenager
OL,11,Fproduced a remarkable turnaround.
OL,13,F"I've definitely learnt a lot,
OL,14,Fespecially with the fans," the 19-year-
OL,15,Fold told a press conference.
OL,17,F"In the first game against (Stephen)
OL,18,FBunting I didn't give anything to the
OL,19,Ffans, I didn't give any reaction and
OL,20,Fgot the job done.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@ZO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
