PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774033869
OL,3,CLuke Littler applies to trademark his
OL,4,Cface to combat AI fakes
OL,6,F"It was the same in the final when I
OL,7,Fwas 5-0 down, everyone doubted me, I
OL,8,Fdefinitely doubted myself but I had a
OL,9,Flittle laugh and a joke. I was just
OL,10,Fhaving a bit of fun because I knew I
OL,11,Fwas beaten.
OL,13,F"I'm still learning not to react to
OL,14,Fthe fans. I didn't do much then, only
OL,15,Ffor the first leg, and then I can
OL,16,Fbuild on it. It is what it is, people
OL,17,Fwant to see new winners but I've won
OL,18,Fagain."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@GO]
